html_attributions: 北京樓 (尖沙咀) Peking Garden Restaurant(Tsimshatsui)

reviews.text: The food was good, but unfortunately the service was extremely disappointing. Two of us ordered : half of Peking Duck, cucumber with in lime chill sauce; braised abalone; sauteed shredded mandarin fish and tan tan noodle. Before the cucumber appetizer came, they brought the duck and all other main courses to the table. When I asked the lady server should appetizer and duck first, she said they brought whatever dishes are ready. We were upset but tried to be accommodating even it was not too busy on this Monday night. The cucumber appetizer we were waiting for,  was known of the cutting skill and presentation. When the server brought it, he did not even give us a chance to take a picture  and started to serve it. We have been dining at this location for a long time, and thus was the worst service we ever had. Please know that no matter how good the food is, it needs to complement with good service
The food here is just absolutely phenomenal. The duck is rich in taste and presentation. This is an easy recommendation to anyone who enjoys Peking duck.
Good place for dinner,food is good, price is above average

It was my first dinner in HK and very impressive. The service is terrible and I seriously don't understand how this restaurant is survived. Even foods are not good enough to cover their awesome service. I strongly suggest you not to visit.

Great spot to try some delicious Peking duck in a more formal environment. Try to make a reservation or arrive early enough to get a table with a view so you can see the evening light show over the water. The dumplings here were fantastic, and the steamed vegetables were really nice as well as a complement to the duck. A bit touristy but still really pleasant environment. Nice for something a little fancy if that's what you're looking for

result.name: 星光行

reviews.text:
老牌商廈，含商場及寫字樓。
亦有幾間美心集團食館及誠品店。地下有麥當奴漢堡飽店。
鄰近天星碼頭，腳程五分鐘可達香港文化中心及香港太空館，廿分鐘可步行至科學舘。
星光行 位於尖沙咀碼頭傍邊 商場面積吾算中型 但冇咩野行 樓上主要是寫字樓 有學聯 有出名的北京樓 但不是人人食得起 場內大部份店舖壽命不長 浪費了－個非常方便之商業地段 ！
觀光旅遊區，頗受遊客歡迎。

北京樓：京菜館子，服務可以，味道質量一般。招牌菜北京填鴨。
店子位於尖沙咀星光行傳統遊客區，租金較高所以碟頭 (份量) 較同系列之其他北京樓少一些。
有製作拉麵表演 (見圖)。
北京樓(星光行)的醬蹄凍象一個小小的荷花池，賣相一流。

以往北京樓，以大集團來講，港式京菜己有9O分。裝修後連菜單都變天，內容係京菜，做法大翻新。當年乞丐雞早改名富貴雞，賣相驚人，內容驚人！真正係富貴人家檯上碟菜！填鴨正常，港式片皮有肉底，薄餅超薄，須小心處理。其他菜式都現代化，但保持舊有影子。須提炸槳麵，北方平民食品變成手エ拉麵，百分百革命，賣相+內容110分。餃子正常，素菜餃一般難做，因北方通行老豆腐干在港難有貨，未食過舊式素餃人仕會接受。集團在尖咀星光行多年值得保留。定位時問清楚セ咭有拆扣，人數多少又有拆扣。此店改變一般人對京菜睇法，值得一試再去，單海邊夜景，己天下無雙！
